@chetanmeh can you take a look into Travis failure, it might be that we are going over the budget 50 minute limit.
>The job exceeded the maximum time limit for jobs, and has been terminated.

I think @houshengbo told me that we are able to have use a Travis matrix and be able to run two jobs in parallel maybe we can run the scan in one and the tests in another one.

@houshengbo do you have an example of such Travis setup?

@rabbah I had made relevant exclude entry in [scanConfig][1] and it works for me. How does your commit hook setup looks like?

I saw this issue when commit hook was not passing the scanConfig path. See also #3295

[1]: https://github.com/apache/incubator-openwhisk/commit/50e5e6c319a2848cfb65089b103bbf1b71193087#diff-11d7cefaf53c9a84b0dc7389fc34335fR34
